{"word":"G370 - ἀνάξιος - anáxios - an-ax'-ee-os - Unworthy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνάξιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anáxios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ax'-ee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unworthy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அபாத்திரமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unworthy, unfit for a thing"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G514 - ἄξιος - áxios - ax'-ee-os/514\">G514</a>; <i>unfit:</i> - unworthy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2661/2661\">G2661</a>, <a href=\"#/G370/370\">G370</a>, <a href=\"#/G514/514\">G514</a>, <a href=\"#/G515/515\">G515</a>"}]}